<h2>Adding Books:</h2>
<p>
dslibris will find all XHTML files with extensions .xht or .xhtml that are in your media's root directory. These books will show up in the book browser.
</p>

<h2>Controls:</h2>
<p>
A/R/PAD-DOWN - forward one page<br/>
B/L/PAD-UP - backward one page<br/>
X - invert text<br/>
Y - change screen brightness<br/>
SELECT - toggle book browser<br/>
</p>

